<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cheer-v">cheer <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tʃɪə(r)/    美 /tʃɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>为...欢呼/喝彩；(为...) 加油：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The fans cheer (for) their team.
粉丝们为自己的队欢呼加油。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="cheer-on">cheer on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>以喝彩声鼓励；为……加油：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father never fails to cheer me on at my sports games.
父亲总是在我参加体育比赛时为我加油。</p><footer>2013 天津改</footer></div>

<h3 id="cheer-up">cheer up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(使) 振作起来；(使) 高兴起来：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She tried to cheer him up.
她努力让他高兴起来。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cheer up! Things will work out for the best.
高兴点儿！事情会圆满解决的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I’m thinking of the test tomorrow. I’m afraid I can’t pass this time.
—<strong><em>_</em></strong>___ (振作点儿)! I’m sure you’ll make it.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Cheer up  </p></div>